item.dc:creator: @KillinXxSMile KillinXxSMile
item.description:
@KillinXxSMile wrote:

looks like a great server,
this is just me but in a server i don’t go for what looks like what i try to do is make things work properly and fix glitches

like for example try to make the pking seem more like the good old rs pking that we all liked.
so pretty much fix up the defense and range etc.

For the fixing glitches if you don’t know what i mean I’m talking about things like the trade dupe(accept and decline) which can be easily fixed.

also if you have done things like this you should really mention it in features it will attract peoples attention and they will appreciate your hard work.

good work and good luck…
